sql:
SELECT id, type_name
FROM pokemon_types
WHERE id = 0;

SELECT DISTINCT pokemon_id
FROM user_interactions
WHERE interaction_type = 'favorite';

SELECT pokemon_id, average_battle_time
FROM battle_statistics
ORDER BY average_battle_time DESC;

SELECT pokemon_id, total_battles
FROM battle_statistics
ORDER BY total_battles DESC;

external_knowledge:
User 1 refers to a specific user in the Pokémon platform; 
Interaction types include view, favorite, catch, etc.;
Battle statistics include wins, losses, draws, total battles, win rate, and average battle time;
Evolution methods include level up, trade, item, etc.;
The identifier is a unique name for each Pokémon species.
